jchrest.lib

Class VisualSpatialFieldObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • jchrest.domainSpecifics.SceneObject
      • jchrest.lib.VisualSpatialFieldObject

  • public class VisualSpatialFieldObject
extends SceneObject
    Represents an object in a VisualSpatialField.

    NOTE: Visual-spatial field objects can not represent SceneObjects whose SceneObject.getObjectType() returns Scene.getBlindSquareToken() since these SceneObjects should be encoded as "unknown" VisualSpatialFieldObjects (see getUnknownSquareToken()).

      • setTerminus

        public void setTerminus(int time,
                        boolean setToTime)
        Parameters:
        time -
        setToTime - Set to Boolean.TRUE to force the terminus of #this to be set to the time specified. Set to Boolean.FALSE to have the method set the terminus according to the recognised status of #this at the time specified:
        • If this #this is recognised, the terminus will be set to the time specified plus the value of Chrest.getRecognisedVisualSpatialFieldObjectLifespan().
        • If this #this is unrecognised, the terminus will be set to the time specified plus the value of Chrest.getUnrecognisedVisualSpatialFieldObjectLifespan().
